\b \cf2 \cell 
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab720\ql\qnatural

\b0 \cf3 In each jar place the following: 1 head of dill, 1 tablespoon of pickling spice, 1 tablespoon of mustard seed, 1 dried chile pepper, and 2 cloves of garlic. Pack beans into the spiced jars in a standing position.\cell \row

