\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab720\ql\qnatural

\b \cf2 \cell 
\pard\intbl\itap1\pardeftab720\ql\qnatural

\b0 \cf3 Ladle the hot brine into jars, leaving 1/2 inch of space at the top. Screw the lids onto the jars, and process in a hot water bath for 6 minutes to seal. Store for at least 2 weeks before eating.\cell \lastrow\row
